GetArgmaxTreatmentsAndMaxLowerBoundsMLE <- function(XX, preds, s = 1.96) {
  dt <- data.table(data.frame(XX, preds))
  dt[, LB:= fit - s * se.fit]
  col_names <- c(grep('^C', names(dt), value = T))
  return (dt[, .(A_pred=A[which.max(LB)], LB_max=max(LB)), by=col_names])
}
